<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Verification Code - Fittingz</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="padding: 40px 20px;">
      <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); overflow: hidden;">
        <!-- Header -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F4C75 0%, #1a5a8a 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
              <div style="display: inline-block; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M2 17L12 22L22 17" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M2 12L12 17L22 12" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Fittingz</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">Fashion Design Platform</p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Body -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 48px 40px;">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
              <div style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%); padding: 12px; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M4 4H20C21.1 4 22 4.9 22 6V18C22 19.1 21.1 20 20 20H4C2.9 20 2 19.1 2 18V6C2 4.9 2.9 4 4 4Z" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M22 6L12 13L2 6" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 style="color: #0F4C75; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">New Verification Code</h2>
              <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; font-weight: 500;">We've generated a fresh code for you</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px; text-align: center;">We've generated a new email verification code for your Fittingz account. Use this code to complete your email verification and activate your account.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e2e8f0 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 280px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;">
                <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">New Verification Code</p>
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F4C75 0%, #1a5a8a 100%); color: #ffffff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; letter-spacing: 4px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(15, 76, 117, 0.3);"><%= verificationCode %></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #b3e5fc 100%); border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 32px 0;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin-right: 12px; margin-top: 2px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                  <path d="M13 16H12V12H11M12 8H12.01M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p style="color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 4px;">Code Information</p>
                  <p style="color: #0369a1; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">This new verification code will expire in <strong>15 minutes</strong>. Your previous verification code is no longer valid. If you didn't request this new code, please ignore this email.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
              <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 16px;">Having trouble with verification?</p>
              <a href="mailto:support@fittingz.com" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e2e8f0 100%); color: #0F4C75; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">Get Help</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 32px 0; text-align: center;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin-right: 8px;">
                  <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <p style="color: #065f46; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0;">Almost there!</p>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #047857; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">Once verified, you'll have full access to all Fittingz features including client management, order tracking, and design tools.</p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%); padding: 32px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 16px; font-weight: 500;">Fittingz &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> - Empowering Fashion Designers</p>
              <div style="margin: 16px 0;">
                <a href="mailto:support@fittingz.com" style="color: #0F4C75; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 16px;">Contact Support</a>
                <span style="color: #cbd5e1;">•</span>
                <a href="#" style="color: #0F4C75; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 16px;">Privacy Policy</a>
                <span style="color: #cbd5e1;">•</span>
                <a href="#" style="color: #0F4C75; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 16px;">Unsubscribe</a>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin: 16px 0 0; line-height: 1.5;">This email was sent because you requested a new verification code.<br/>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>